{"tid":2411370,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"何超儀自資在港拍荷李活片 重金聘奧斯卡導演執導","createTime":"2021-02-17T09:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T13:58:31.000Z","uid":130626,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"303421a3d8c2278aa16fcbbb883ef670151a2fc5","tid":2411370,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T09:35:45.000Z","msg":"何超儀（Josie）在疫情下自資開拍一齣荷李活電影《Mother Tongue》，邀請了奧斯卡金像獎導演Mike Figgis及多位國際影星，包括濱邊美波、Julian Sands、Tomoko Nawata及金燕玲演出。今次製作邀請了藉名小說作家Bruce Wagner編寫電影故事。<br />\n<br />\nJosie透露，新片原定在美國開拍，但礙於當地疫情嚴峻，故移師到香港拍攝，並在邵氏片廠搭出超巨型美式大宅入為主要場景，電影以全英語對白拍攝。Josie今日聯同擔任監製的老公陳子聰及導演Mike Figgis，帶領着劇組一同在邵氏片廠進行開鏡拜神儀式。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210217/X2JVFDY7ZJD45AR7DHN2UDB2F4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210217%2FX2JVFDY7ZJD45AR7DHN2UDB2F4%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN24PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=37079a1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210217%2FX2JVFDY7ZJD45AR7DHN2UDB2F4%2F&h=a961b213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210217/X2JVFDY7ZJD45AR7DHN2UDB2F4/</a>"},{"pid":"ab65140e53778d6cacf73ef1b4392af2320db7b8","tid":2411370,"uid":4574,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T09:39:03.000Z","msg":"美波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1366f773dd17a60e183b41757039db55d42adc0","tid":2411370,"uid":313584,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T09:59:06.000Z","msg":"金燕玲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e0df210b3c45f98801e9c37ee915ea7a977309","tid":2411370,"uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:00:55.000Z","msg":"Mike Figgis 即係拍尼古拉斯基治好撚depressed嗰套 兩顆絕望的心 嘅導演<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16be5e4f2c9b